---
---
<section id="contact" class="contact">
  <div class="contact-bg-text" aria-hidden="true">TALK</div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-top" data-reveal>
      <span class="section-label">Contacto</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="contact-heading font-display" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
      <span class="line">¿Tenés un</span>
      <span class="line indent">proyecto</span>
      <span class="line outline-word">EN MENTE?</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="contact-body">
      <p class="contact-sub" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">
        Contame de qué se trata.<br />Te respondo con lo que necesitás saber.
      </p>

      <div class="contact-links" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
        <a href="https://wa.me/595982531706" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-link" data-cursor="hover" data-tilt>
          <span class="link-label">WhatsApp</span>
          <span class="link-val">+595 982 531 706</span>
          <span class="link-arr">↗</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://instagram.com/its_csdev" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-link" data-cursor="hover" data-tilt>
          <span class="link-label">Instagram</span>
          <span class="link-val">@its_csdev</span>
          <span class="link-arr">↗</span>
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:contactame@csdev.qzz.io" class="contact-link" data-cursor="hover" data-tilt>
          <span class="link-label">Email</span>
          <span class="link-val">contactame@csdev.qzz.io</span>
          <span class="link-arr">↗</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact {
    padding: 8rem 0 6rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 80vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .contact-bg-text {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -3rem;
    right: -3rem;
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(10rem, 24vw, 24rem);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .container { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  .contact-top { margin-bottom: 2rem; }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .contact-heading {
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 9vw, 10rem);
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .contact-heading .line { display: block; }
  .contact-heading .indent { padding-left: clamp(2rem, 12vw, 14rem); }

  .outline-word {
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 3px var(--black);
  }

  .contact-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .contact-sub {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .contact-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

  .contact-link {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    cursor: none;
    transition: padding-left 0.25s;
  }

  .contact-link:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
  .contact-link:hover { padding-left: 1rem; }
  .contact-link:hover .link-arr { opacity: 1; transform: translate(2px, -2px); }

  .link-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .link-val {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .link-arr {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translate(-4px, 4px);
    transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.25s;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .contact-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .contact-link { grid-template-columns: 90px 1fr auto; }
    .link-arr { opacity: 0.5; transform: none; }
    .outline-word { -webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--black); }
  }
</style>
